To create a snap-to experience for the infinite scroll video feed, you can use CSS Scroll Snap Points. This will ensure that when the user scrolls through the video feed, each video will snap into place, occupying the entire viewport.

First, in `Home.svelte`, update the `ul` element to use a CSS class named `video-feed`:
```html
<ul id="video-list" class="video-feed">
  {#each videos as video}
    <li>
